text: Bhai, Tera memoir last hai, isko likhne ke baad energy nahi bachegi. Aaj bhi yad hai first din jab mile the wing me, tu bc typiical brown munde ki tarah kharkate kar raha tha. Fir treasure hunt me pure time tune gaand tow kari meri, launde aaye aur chale gaye apne group me lekin you were constant bro, tu last kar lekar hi gaya. First midsem me tere sasth padhayi kari thi PHY ki, mai padhne baitha tha tune kaha tha chal tehel ke aate hai, fir apan khane pine gaye the, maine kaha tha padh lete hai tune kaha chod maine bhi nahi padha, mai chill ho gaya tha fir. Fir jab exam me marks aaaye to 3 idiots ke us scene ka ache se realization hua xD Madarchod to tu tha, bsdka sab padh leta tha aur na padhne ki acting karta tha. Winter vacations me pehla londa tha tu IIT K ka jisko call kiya tha, aur ab bhi kisi ko call karu na ya karu tereko jarur karta hu. Mujhe humesha se pata tha tera double dassa aega. Ab sochta hu agar na aata to zada better tha, tu bhi apni gang me ajata, padhayi kam aur bakchodi zada karta. Tu hi saccha dost tha bhai, saari baate batayi, sath me RR kiya ladkiyo ka. Teri wo 4 ladkio ki baate abhi bhi yaad hai, naam nahi bhulta tha mai acting karta tha bhulne ki xD Dono ko realize to ho hi gaya tha "these hoes ain't loyal" Us time tu daaru pita hota to badhiya maze karte hum dono :P. 1st year ke baad thoda hangout hona kam ho gaya lekin fir bhi tere room pe aake wo RR karna humesha constant tha. Late night canteen jana ho ya cycle banwane ka ya kahi bhi idhar udhar, thoda nakhre karne ke baad tu finally chal to deta ha. Mujhe lagta hai tu ek character play karta hai rough boy banne ka jo tu hai nahi, bc aandar se tu bhi bht soft hearted hai. Intern lagne ke baad jab tune daru pi thi to tujhse zada mai khush hua tha bhai. SPO ki history me sabse corrupt IC me tera naam top par hoga, ğŸ˜‚ Tu hi ek akela banda tha jsike room pe kabhi bhi knock kardo bhale hi bande ki ma chudi padi ho lekin room khol jarur dega, chidh ke tu gussse me bakchodi kardeta tha cycle ke liye lekin chill hai teri baato ka bura nahi lagta tha kabhi ğŸ˜‚ First year me mere room wale kisse bhi yaad ate hai, bc Aakarsh se lad baitha tha jhaat bhar ki baat ke liye. Election me tune bhi top level politics kari hai, aadha credit to tujhe dena chahiye jeetne ka ğŸ˜› Course me cheating karvana ho ya assignment likhwana ho, nakhre jitne bhi karle lekin kabhi mana nahi kiya bhaiâ¤ï¸ I am so lucky that the first friend I made here is still one of my good firends. Abhi to zindagi kaafi bachi hai, milna julna laga rahega (I very strongly hope this). Aur apna character chodh de bhai, koi judge nahi karega, karega bhi to uski maa ka bhosdağŸš¬ğŸ’‹

Nannu MC. Tu to likhega nahi memoir, mai hi likh deta hu. Bahot madarchod hai tu. Apne aap ko baap samajhta hai, lekin tu chota don hi hai, teri height mujhse choti hai.

Click bait to ho gaya ab asli memoir start karta hu :P Bhai hazaro kisse hai, tujhe kitna bhi lodu bolu mai lekin to IIT K me sabse zada chaapu launda hai, Jaha gaya hai tune waha minimum effort ke saath sabki gaande fadi hai. Ye skill sabme nahi hoti bhai. Tujhe main genuinely baccha samajhta tha, lekin wo December protest ke baad tere liye god level respect agayi thi bhi. Us situation me bade bado ka moot nikal jaye, tune to makkhan handle karliya. Wo din mai kabhi nahi bhulunga. Apne hall ka londa jo GPL me bat lekar ajata hai khudko bachane, wo Kanpur ke SSP ko bol raha hai ham nahi hatenge jo ukhad pao ukhad lo. bhai us din laga ki is londe me dam hai, ma chod dega kisi ki. Tu na hota to aaj SSAC kya jail me baithe hote hum jaise kuch launde :P I don't think humdono me difference hue kabhi, tera aur mera nature bahot different hai isliye kabhi kabhi thoda south chala jata tha apna discussion, lekin wo bhi chill hai bhai â¤ï¸ Tujhe dil se bhai maana hai. Kitne sapne dekhe the bhai, Shapatgrahan samaroh karvaenge, murtiya staphit karvaenge.. :') Ye sab soch ke bht BT hoti hai, Kaash ye covid ka chutiyap na hota, Tere pe pura bharosa tha tu campus badal deta. AB lagta hai thoda aur bakchodi karni chahiye thi saath me, ek dusri ki gaand marne se focus hata ke badia memories banani chahiye thi. Chill hai, I hope ki aage iska bhi time aaga.
